For example, I have been told that I bribe the journalists or that I was the advisor to Jiří Paroubek.
Now to your visions.
You have begun the struggle for the Castle with the themes of the material and criminal responsibility of politicians and retroactive tax declarations beyond twenty million [CZK] as your workhorse.
